	<clause id="_determination_of_the_required_quantities_and_the_associated_uncertainty_evaluation" obligation="normative"><title>Determination of the required quantities and the associated uncertainty evaluation</title><p id="_7cead701-c174-4ef8-a3c1-53b2bd3af869">The primary quantities of interest are</p>
	<ul id="_cf52ab58-9afd-4d20-a311-c5a02e751f43">
